# starlette 0.52.1 — transitive via apache-airflow's FastAPI API server.
# The fixed versions (1.1.0 / 1.3.1) are starlette 1.x, which the *pinned*
# apache-airflow 3.2.1 / FastAPI stack does not yet support (it constrains
# starlette < 1.0 — `uv lock --upgrade-package starlette` cannot move it).
# Risk accepted: the Airflow API server is bound to localhost only (not
# published — see docker-compose port notes), and the StaticFiles SSRF / UNC
# vector requires serving static files from attacker-controlled paths, which
# this stack does not do.
# REMOVE when apache-airflow ships a FastAPI that supports starlette >= 1.3.1.
CVE-2026-48818
CVE-2026-54283
